sequenceDiagram
    actor Donor
    participant Frontend
    participant FastAPI
    participant Razorpay
    participant Database

    Donor->>Frontend: Select NGO and amount
    Frontend->>FastAPI: POST /donations/create-order
    FastAPI->>Razorpay: Create Order via SDK
    Razorpay-->>FastAPI: order_id + amount
    FastAPI->>Database: INSERT Donation (status=Pending)
    FastAPI-->>Frontend: order_id + key_id
    Frontend->>Razorpay: Open Checkout Widget
    Donor->>Razorpay: Complete Payment (UPI/Card)
    Razorpay-->>Frontend: payment_id + signature
    Frontend->>FastAPI: POST /donations/verify-payment
    FastAPI->>Razorpay: Verify HMAC-SHA256 signature
    Razorpay-->>FastAPI: Valid
    FastAPI->>Database: UPDATE Donation status=Success
    FastAPI-->>Frontend: Payment verified
    Frontend-->>Donor: Thank you! Donation Successful
